One Time Pad Utilities

The one time pad utilities has no external dependencies so you should
find that building for your favorite platform is easy and quick.  If
you run into problems building the binaries please drop me a note and
I will do my best to fix any porting issues and get those fixes back
into the tree.  Even better...send me your fixes :)

Dependencies
------------
- modern incarnation of gcc (or similar C compiler)
- make
